The paper discusses the use of hypernetworks to generate and train neural networks for various tasks, including image representation and generative modeling. This makes it likely to fall under the categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE), and graphics (cs.GR).
